text: Shop Owner: Everyone is doing the same type of biryani in chennai, So we tried a different of biryani for our people
This is started by our friends as passion
90's Kids Friends
No one is providing such Bamboo Biryani concept in this area, so tried this and its around 25 days over since we started
When we started our business was slightly dull because people need to understand its best in quality and taste.
Now we selling this biryani and winding up with 2 hours itself
And some people does not get the biryani as its sold out soon nowadays
Per day we are selling around 25 to 30 kgs of Biryani
3 pcs chicken + Egg we are giving it for 99Rs  We don't charge anything takeaway as well, customers satisfaction is our main goal.
Customer Review: I use to travel in this way, since its looks different i tried it, and taste is good even chicken pieces are also cooked properly
Customer Review: I did not try Bamboo Biryani before, its new experience for me in taste.
Customer Review: Next Level and taste is super.
